            . I am servant to Mr. Mabberly of Paul's Wharf; we deal with the prosecutor. On the 25th of March I paid the prisoner a banker's draft for 2 l., on Messrs. Masterman, and produce the receipt he gave me - (read) - sometime after the prosecutor called for it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190915-91-person813">
