             re-examined. He never gave me the draft, nor accounted to me for it. I particularly questioned him about it, and he said he had not received it.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181909150029"></xptr>Prisoner's Defence. My master stopped my last week's wages. I thought that was for part of it.</p>

